					<div>
						<pb n="3"/><p><lb/>In <placeName ref="loc007683.17">Zollets thurn</placeName>
							<seg><lb/><origDate when="1618-08-25">25<hi rend="sup">ten</hi> <foreign xml:lang="la">augusti</foreign> <hi rend="underline">1618</hi></origDate>, <foreign xml:lang="la">presentibus</foreign> </seg>
							<seg><lb/><foreign xml:lang="la"><choice><abbr>Jud</abbr><expan>Judice</expan></choice></foreign> <abbr>h</abbr> <choice><abbr>groß</abbr> <expan>großweibel</expan></choice><note>Gemeint ist <persName ref="per009391">Wilhelm Reynold</persName>.</note></seg>
							<seg><lb/><abbr>H</abbr> <persName ref="per009250">Gerwer</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009388"><choice><abbr>P</abbr><expan>Peter</expan></choice> Reyff</persName>, <persName ref="per009579a.01"><choice><abbr>Lud</abbr><expan>Ludwig</expan></choice> Gotrou</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/><persName ref="per009259a.01">Ligertz</persName>, <persName ref="per009123">Werly</persName></seg>
							<seg><lb/>Weybel</seg></p>
						<p><gap reason="irrelevant"/><note>Der erste Abschnitt betrifft den Prozess gegen <persName ref="per009583">Jenon Rey</persName>. Vgl. <ref target="urn:ssrq:SSRQ-FR-I_2_8-41.3-1">SSRQ FR I/2/8 41.3-1</ref>.</note></p>
						<p><lb/><foreign xml:lang="la">Ibidem die, anno et presentibus
							<lb/>quibus supra</foreign><note><persName ref="per009584a">Joni Voland</persName> wurde ebenfalls im <placeName ref="loc007683.15">Zolletsturm</placeName> verhört.</note></p>
						<p><seg><lb/><add place="left margin"><foreign xml:lang="la"><choice><abbr>ßt</abbr><expan>Solvit</expan></choice></foreign> <measure type="currency" unit="lb" quantity="3">3 </measure>.</add></seg>
							<seg><persName ref="per009584a">Joni Voland</persName> de <placeName ref="loc007660">La Roche</placeName>, sortie de la mayson
						<lb/>des <persName>Jerly</persName>, s’esmerveillant de l’apprisonnement,
						<lb/>nye savoir aulcunes <choice><abbr>supstions</abbr><expan>superstitions</expan></choice>, mesmement per<lb break="no"/>sonne ne l’avoir veu de nuict i faire aulcun
						<lb/>mal. Touttesfois estre vray, estre esté taxee par
								<lb/><persName>Bally</persName>, <term ref="lem019389.02">sorciere</term>, mais luy avoir reparé par deux
						<lb/>hommes son honneur. Plus elle nye avoir dict que
								<lb/>si elle est <term ref="lem019389.02">sorciere</term>, de vouloir fournir le bois
								<pb n="4"/><lb/>pour la <term ref="lem019496.02">bruler</term>. N’avoir onques <term ref="lem015635.24">ballé</term> rien du mal aux
						<lb/>enfants, que de la viande aux siens. Et estant
						<lb/><term ref="lem018774.03">admonestee</term> de prier, ne sa<subst><del>it</del><add place="overwritten">voit</add></subst> prier que en latin, et
								<lb/><add place="left margin"><hi rend="underline">encores</hi></add> de nulle valeur. Elle a dict ne cognoistre aultre<lb break="no"/>ment la femme de <persName ref="per009585">Gauzon</persName>. Aultre n’a dict.<note>Der nächste Abschnitt betrifft den Prozess gegen <persName ref="per009582a.01">Clauda Grandjean</persName>. Vgl. <ref target="urn:ssrq:SSRQ-FR-I_2_8-42.1-1">SSRQ FR I/2/8 42.1-1</ref>.</note></seg></p>
					</div>
